piece.name: frm_tezza_form_init_campos
piece.title: Llenar inicio formulario
piece.description: Código para llenar campos varios de un formulario al cargar
piece.code:
$this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_InitLib\x27)\x3B

$this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_addCustomCSSFile\x27)\x3B
ff_addCustomCSSFile(\x27components/com_frmtezza/css/style.css\x27)\x3B

$db = JFactory::getDbo()\x3B
$user = JFactory::getUser()\x3B

// Validar usuario registrado
if ( ! $user-\x3Eid ){
 header(\x27Location: \x27. JURI::base())\x3B
 exit()\x3B
}

// -- Datos de Area y Nombre usuario --

$query = $db-\x3EgetQuery(true)\x3B
$query-\x3Eselect(\x27*\x27)
 -\x3Efrom($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27#__frmtezza_v_user_area\x27))
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27user_id\x27) . \x27 = \x27.$user-\x3Eid)
 -\x3EsetLimit(1)\x3B

$db-\x3EsetQuery($query)\x3B
$area = $db-\x3EloadObject()\x3B

ff_setValue(\x27area\x27\x2C $area-\x3Etitle)\x3B
ff_setValue(\x27nombres\x27\x2C$user-\x3Ename)\x3B

if ( ! $area ) ff_setValue(\x27nombres\x27\x2C\x27Error - El usuario tiene que tener un área asignada\x27)\x3B

// -- Datos adicionales campos personalizados Codigo\x2C Documento\x2C Cargo --

$query = $db-\x3EgetQuery(true)\x3B

$query-\x3Eselect(array(\x27f.name\x27\x2C \x27f.title\x27\x2C \x27v.value\x27))
 -\x3Efrom($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27#__fields\x27\x2C\x27f\x27))
 -\x3Ejoin(\x27INNER\x27\x2C $db-\x3EquoteName(\x27#__fields_values\x27\x2C\x27v\x27).\x27 ON \x27.$db-\x3EquoteName(\x27f.id\x27).\x27=\x27.$db-\x3EquoteName(\x27v.field_id\x27))
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27v.item_id\x27).\x27=\x27.$user-\x3Eid)\x3B

$db-\x3EsetQuery($query)\x3B
$user_data = $db-\x3EloadAssocList(\x27name\x27\x2C \x27value\x27)\x3B

if ($user_data){
 if ( isset($user_data[\x27codigo\x27]) ) ff_setValue(\x27codigo\x27\x2C$user_data[\x27codigo\x27])\x3B
 if ( isset($user_data[\x27documento\x27]) ) ff_setValue(\x27numerodocumento\x27\x2C$user_data[\x27documento\x27])\x3B
 if ( isset($user_data[\x27descripcion-de-cargo\x27]) ) ff_setValue(\x27cargo\x27\x2C$user_data[\x27descripcion-de-cargo\x27])\x3B
}



// -- Obtener el ID del área de Jefes

$query = $db-\x3EgetQuery(true)\x3B
$query-\x3Eselect(array(\x27id\x27))
 -\x3Efrom($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27#__usergroups\x27))
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27title\x27) . \x22 LIKE \x27%Area%JEFE%\x27\x22)
 -\x3EsetLimit(1)\x3B

$db-\x3EsetQuery($query)\x3B

$area_jefes = $db-\x3EloadResult()\x3B
$area_user = $area-\x3Egroup_id\x3B
$id_jefe = 0\x3B

// -- Obtener el ID del jefe de área

$subQuery = $db-\x3EgetQuery(true)\x3B
$query = $db-\x3EgetQuery(true)\x3B

// Create the base subQuery select statement.
$subQuery-\x3Eselect(array(\x27user_id\x27))
 -\x3Efrom($db-\x3EquoteName($db-\x3EgetPrefix().\x27user_usergroup_map\x27))
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27group_id\x27) . \x27 = \x27 . $area_jefes)\x3B

// Create the base select statement.
$query-\x3Eselect(array(\x27user_id\x27))
 -\x3Efrom($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27#__frmtezza_v_user_area\x27))
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27group_id\x27) . \x27 = \x27 . $area_user)
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27user_id\x27) . \x27 IN (\x27 . $subQuery . \x27)\x27)\x3B

// Validacion area
if ( $area ) {
 $db-\x3EsetQuery($query)\x3B
 $id_jefe = $db-\x3EloadResult()\x3B
 
 ff_setValue(\x27id_jefe\x27\x2C$id_jefe)\x3B //Asignar el valor del id jefe al campo
}

piece.name: frm_tezza_llenar_tabla_bd
piece.title: Llenar tabla y enviar mail
piece.description: Código para actualizar la tabla de integración de la extensión frmtezza con BF
piece.code:
$this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_InitLib\x27)\x3B

// Get user area\x2C filter the first area
$db = JFactory::getDbo()\x3B
$query = $db-\x3EgetQuery(true)\x3B

$user =JFactory::getUser()\x3B
$area = 0\x3B

// Validar usuario registrado
if ( ! $user-\x3Eid ){
 header(\x27Location: \x27. JURI::base())\x3B
 exit()\x3B
}

$query-\x3Eselect(\x27group_id\x27)
 -\x3Efrom($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27#__frmtezza_v_user_area\x27))
 -\x3Ewhere($db-\x3EquoteName(\x27user_id\x27) . \x27 = \x27.$user-\x3Eid)
 -\x3EsetLimit(1)\x3B

$db-\x3EsetQuery($query)\x3B
$area = $db-\x3EloadResult()\x3B


$data =new stdClass()\x3B
$data-\x3Eid_user = $user-\x3Eid\x3B
$data-\x3Eid_record = $this-\x3Erecord_id\x3B
$data-\x3Eid_area = $area\x3B

$db-\x3EinsertObject( \x27#__frmtezza_frm_user\x27\x2C $data )\x3B


// Enviar correo

$title = JFactory::getDocument()-\x3EgetTitle()\x3B
$url = JURI::base().\x22administracion-formularios.html\x22\x3B
$id_jefe = ff_getSubmit(\x27id_jefe\x27)\x3B
$user_jefe = JFactory::getUser($id_jefe)\x3B

$config = JFactory::getConfig()\x3B
$sender = array(
 $config-\x3Eget( \x27mailfrom\x27 )\x2C
 $config-\x3Eget( \x27fromname\x27 )
)\x3B

$recipient1 = $user-\x3Eemail\x3B
$recipient2 = $user_jefe-\x3Eemail\x3B

if ( $recipient1 ){
 $subject = \x22Creaste una nueva solicitud - \x22.$title\x3B
 $body = \x22\x3Cp\x3EPuedes hacer un seguimiento de la solicitud de \x22.$title.\x22 en la intranet\x3C/p\x3E\x22\x3B
 $body .= \x22\x3Ca href=\x27\x22.$url.\x22\x27 target=\x27_blank\x27\x3EVer Solicitud\x3C/a\x3E\x22\x3B

 $mailer1 = JFactory::getMailer()\x3B
 $mailer1-\x3EisHtml(true)\x3B
 $mailer1-\x3EEncoding = \x27base64\x27\x3B

 $mailer1-\x3EsetSender($sender)\x3B
 $mailer1-\x3EaddRecipient( $recipient1 )\x3B

 $mailer1-\x3EsetSubject($subject)\x3B
 $mailer1-\x3EsetBody($body)\x3B

 $mailer1-\x3ESend()\x3B
}

if ( $recipient2){
 $subject = \x22Una solicitud de \x22.$title.\x22 esta esperando tu aprobación\x22\x3B
 $body = \x22\x3Cp\x3EPuedes ver la nueva solicidud de \x22.$title.\x22 creada por \x22.$user-\x3Ename.\x22 en la intranet\x3C/p\x3E\x22\x3B
 $body .= \x22\x3Ca href=\x27\x22.$url.\x22\x27 target=\x27_blank\x27\x3EVer Solicitud\x3C/a\x3E\x22\x3B

 $mailer2 = JFactory::getMailer()\x3B
 $mailer2-\x3EisHtml(true)\x3B
 $mailer2-\x3EEncoding = \x27base64\x27\x3B

 $mailer2-\x3EsetSender($sender)\x3B
 $mailer2-\x3EaddRecipient( $recipient2 )\x3B

 $mailer2-\x3EsetSubject($subject)\x3B
 $mailer2-\x3EsetBody($body)\x3B

 $mailer2-\x3ESend()\x3B
}
